Package: agent-studio-open
Version: 0.2.0
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: AuraOne Open Studio <opensource@auraone.ai>
Homepage: https://agentstudio.auraone.ai/
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/auraoneai/agent-studio-open
Depends: libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0 | libwebkit2gtk-4.0-37, libayatana-appindicator3-1, librsvg2-2, ca-certificates
Description: Local-first IDE for debugging MCP and A2A agents
 Agent Studio Open records, replays, compares, and regression-tests
 MCP and A2A agent sessions locally. It stores traces on disk,
 keeps user secrets in the OS keychain, and uses opt-in telemetry only.
